"""
google_agent/source/knowledge_graph_agent.py
===============================================================================
KnowledgeGraphAgent V47 — clean ADK/Gemini KG only.

No monkey patch.
No BaseAgent change.
No deterministic fallback graph.
No emergency graph.
No hardcoded Star/Galaxy/Snowflake rule.

KG job:
- read selectedNode
- read RAG/source buckets
- read ConceptExtraction concepts
- read full structured Vision packet
- carry local PDF image pointers
- carry MongoDB MCP proof
- ask ADK/Gemini for concept relationship graph
- normalize/guard output
- fail honestly if unusable

Important:
- RAG text = source truth.
- Vision = visual truth.
- If RAG misses a visual relation, keep it as evidenceType="vision_only".
- vision_only can guide board/teacher path, but sourceProof must be empty.
===============================================================================
"""

